= SDL_LockMutex =
Use this function to lock a mutex created with [[SDL_CreateMutex]]().


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_LockMutex(SDL_mutex* mutex)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''mutex''' 
|the mutex to lock
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

